{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Once upon a time, there was a dread disease that afflicted children."},{"time":5000,"text":"And in fact, among all the diseases that existed in this land,"},{"time":9000,"text":"it was the worst. It killed the most children."},{"time":12000,"text":"And along came a brilliant inventor, a scientist,"},{"time":15000,"text":"who came up with a partial cure for that disease."},{"time":18000,"text":"And it wasn't perfect. Many children still died,"},{"time":22000,"text":"but it was certainly better than what they had before."},{"time":25000,"text":"And one of the good things about this cure was that it was free,"},{"time":31000,"text":"virtually free, and was very easy to use."},{"time":33000,"text":"But the worst thing about it was that you couldn't use it"},{"time":36000,"text":"on the youngest children, on infants, and on one-year-olds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40000,"text":"And so, as a consequence, a few years later,"},{"time":42000,"text":"another scientist -- perhaps maybe this scientist"},{"time":44000,"text":"not quite as brilliant as the one who had preceded him,"},{"time":48000,"text":"but building on the invention of the first one --"},{"time":50000,"text":"came up with a second cure."},{"time":53000,"text":"And the beauty of the second cure for this disease"},{"time":56000,"text":"was that it could be used on infants and one-year-olds."},{"time":60000,"text":"And the problem with this cure was it was very expensive,"},{"time":65000,"text":"and it was very complicated to use."},{"time":66000,"text":"And although parents tried as hard as they could to use it properly,"},{"time":70000,"text":"almost all of them ended up using it wrong in the end."},{"time":74000,"text":"But what they did, of course, since it was so complicated and expensive,"},{"time":77000,"text":"they only used it on the zero-year-olds and the one-year-olds."},{"time":80000,"text":"And they kept on using the existing cure that they had"},{"time":83000,"text":"on the two-year-olds and up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84000,"text":"And this went on for quite some time. People were happy."},{"time":86000,"text":"They had their two cures. Until a particular mother,"},{"time":89000,"text":"whose child had just turned two, died of this disease."},{"time":94000,"text":"And she thought to herself, \"My child just turned two,"},{"time":98000,"text":"and until the child turned two, I had always used"},{"time":102000,"text":"this complicated, expensive cure, you know, this treatment."},{"time":107000,"text":"And then the child turned two, and I started using"},{"time":108000,"text":"the cheap and easy treatment, and I wonder\" --"},{"time":111000,"text":"and she wondered, like all parents who lose children wonder --"},{"time":113000,"text":"\"if there isn't something that I could have done,"},{"time":115000,"text":"like keep on using that complicated, expensive cure.\""},{"time":119000,"text":"And she told all the other people, and she said,"},{"time":122000,"text":"\"How could it possibly be that something"},{"time":124000,"text":"that's cheap and simple works as well as something"},{"time":127000,"text":"that's complicated and expensive?\""},{"time":129000,"text":"And the people thought, \"You know, you're right."},{"time":131000,"text":"It probably is the wrong thing to do to switch"},{"time":133000,"text":"and use the cheap and simple solution.\""},{"time":136000,"text":"And the government, they heard her story and the other people,"},{"time":139000,"text":"and they said, \"Yeah, you're right, we should make a law."},{"time":142000,"text":"We should outlaw this cheap and simple treatment"},{"time":144000,"text":"and not let anybody use this on their children.\""},{"time":147000,"text":"And the people were happy. They were satisfied."}]},{"cues":[{"time":149000,"text":"For many years this went along, and everything was fine."},{"time":152000,"text":"But then along came a lowly economist, who had children himself,"},{"time":157000,"text":"and he used the expensive and complicated treatment."},{"time":164000,"text":"But he knew about the cheap and simple one."},{"time":166000,"text":"And he thought about it, and the expensive one"},{"time":168000,"text":"didn't seem that great to him. So he thought,"},{"time":171000,"text":"\"I don't know anything about science, but I do know something about data,"},{"time":174000,"text":"so maybe I should go and look at the data"},{"time":176000,"text":"and see whether this expensive and complicated treatment"},{"time":180000,"text":"actually works any better than the cheap and simple one.\""},{"time":183000,"text":"And lo and behold, when he went through the data,"},{"time":185000,"text":"he found that it didn't look like the expensive, complicated"},{"time":188000,"text":"solution was any better than the cheap one,"},{"time":191000,"text":"at least for the children who were two and older --"},{"time":193000,"text":"the cheap one still didn't work on the kids who were younger."}]},{"cues":[{"time":196000,"text":"And so, he went forth to the people and he said,"},{"time":200000,"text":"\"I've made this wonderful finding:"},{"time":202000,"text":"it looks as if we could just use the cheap and simple solution,"},{"time":205000,"text":"and by doing so we could save ourselves 300 million dollars a year,"},{"time":208000,"text":"and we could spend that on our children in other ways.\""},{"time":210000,"text":"And the parents were very unhappy, and they said,"},{"time":214000,"text":"\"This is a terrible thing, because how can the cheap and easy thing"},{"time":216000,"text":"be as good as the hard thing?\" And the government was very upset."},{"time":220000,"text":"And in particular, the people who made this expensive solution"},{"time":223000,"text":"were very upset because they thought,"},{"time":225000,"text":"\"How can we hope to compete with something that's essentially free?"},{"time":228000,"text":"We would lose all of our market.\""},{"time":230000,"text":"And people were very angry, and they called him horrible names."},{"time":233000,"text":"And he decided that maybe he should leave the country"},{"time":236000,"text":"for a few days, and seek out some more intelligent,"},{"time":240000,"text":"open-minded people in a place called Oxford,"},{"time":243000,"text":"and come and try and tell the story at that place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246000,"text":"And so, anyway, here I am. It's not a fairy tale."},{"time":250000,"text":"It's a true story about the United States today,"},{"time":252000,"text":"and the disease I'm referring to is actually"},{"time":255000,"text":"motor vehicle accidents for children."},{"time":258000,"text":"And the free cure is adult seatbelts, and the expensive cure --"},{"time":264000,"text":"the 300-million-dollar-a-year cure -- is child car seats."},{"time":268000,"text":"And what I'd like to talk to you about today"},{"time":270000,"text":"is some of the evidence why I believe this to be true:"},{"time":273000,"text":"that for children two years old and up,"},{"time":275000,"text":"there really is no real benefit -- proven benefit -- of car seats,"},{"time":280000,"text":"in spite of the incredible energy"},{"time":285000,"text":"that has been devoted toward expanding the laws"},{"time":288000,"text":"and making it socially unacceptable"},{"time":290000,"text":"to put your children into seatbelts. And then talk about why --"},{"time":295000,"text":"what is it that makes that true?"},{"time":296000,"text":"And then, finally talk a little bit about a third way,"},{"time":299000,"text":"about another technology, which is probably better than anything we have,"},{"time":302000,"text":"but which -- there hasn't been any enthusiasm for adoption"},{"time":305000,"text":"precisely because people are so enamored"},{"time":307000,"text":"with the current car seat solution. OK."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310000,"text":"So, many times when you try to do research on data,"},{"time":313000,"text":"it records complicated stories -- it's hard to find in the data."},{"time":317000,"text":"It doesn't turn out to be the case when you look at seatbelts versus car seats."},{"time":320000,"text":"So the United States keeps a data set"},{"time":322000,"text":"of every fatal accident that's happened since 1975."},{"time":325000,"text":"So in every car crash in which at least one person dies,"},{"time":328000,"text":"they have information on all of the people."},{"time":330000,"text":"So if you look at that data -- it's right up on the National Highway"},{"time":333000,"text":"Transportation Safety Administration's website --"},{"time":335000,"text":"you can just look at the raw data,"},{"time":337000,"text":"and begin to get a sense of the limited amount of evidence"},{"time":341000,"text":"that's in favor of car seats for children aged two and up."},{"time":344000,"text":"So, here is the data. Here I have, among two- to six-year-olds --"},{"time":348000,"text":"anyone above six, basically no one uses car seats,"},{"time":350000,"text":"so you can't compare -- 29.3 percent of the children who are unrestrained"},{"time":356000,"text":"in a crash in which at least one person dies, themselves die."},{"time":360000,"text":"If you put a child in a car seat, 18.2 percent of the children die."},{"time":365000,"text":"If they're wearing a lap-and-shoulder belt, in this raw data,"},{"time":367000,"text":"19.4 percent die. And interestingly, wearing a lap-only seatbelt,"},{"time":372000,"text":"16.7 percent die. And actually, the theory tells you"},{"time":374000,"text":"that the lap-only seatbelt's got to be worse"},{"time":377000,"text":"than the lap-and-shoulder belt. And that just reminds you"},{"time":378000,"text":"that when you deal with raw data, there are hundreds"},{"time":380000,"text":"of confounding variables that may be getting in the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":383000,"text":"So what we do in the study is -- and this is just presenting"},{"time":388000,"text":"the same information, but turned into a figure to make it easier."},{"time":391000,"text":"So the yellow bar represents car seats,"},{"time":394000,"text":"the orange bar lap-and-shoulder, and the red bar lap-only seatbelts."},{"time":398000,"text":"And this is all relative to unrestrained --"},{"time":400000,"text":"the bigger the bar, the better. Okay."},{"time":401000,"text":"So, this is the data I just showed, OK?"},{"time":403000,"text":"So the highest bar is what you're striving to beat."},{"time":406000,"text":"So you can control for the basic things, like how hard the crash was,"},{"time":410000,"text":"what seat the child was sitting in, etc., the age of the child."},{"time":414000,"text":"And that's that middle set of bars."},{"time":416000,"text":"And so, you can see that the lap-only seatbelts"},{"time":419000,"text":"start to look worse once you do that."},{"time":421000,"text":"And then finally, the last set of bars,"},{"time":423000,"text":"which are really controlling for everything"},{"time":426000,"text":"you could possibly imagine about the crash,"},{"time":428000,"text":"50, 75, 100 different characteristics of the crash."}]},{"cues":[{"time":431000,"text":"And what you find is that the car seats and the lap-and-shoulder belts,"},{"time":434000,"text":"when it comes to saving lives, fatalities look exactly identical."},{"time":438000,"text":"And the standard error bands are relatively small around these estimates as well."},{"time":442000,"text":"And it's not just overall. It's very robust"},{"time":445000,"text":"to anything you want to look at."},{"time":447000,"text":"One thing that's interesting: if you look at frontal-impact crashes --"},{"time":450000,"text":"when the car crashes, the front hits into something --"},{"time":453000,"text":"indeed, what you see is that the car seats look a little bit better."},{"time":457000,"text":"And I think this isn't just chance."},{"time":459000,"text":"In order to have the car seat approved,"},{"time":460000,"text":"you need to pass certain federal standards,"},{"time":463000,"text":"all of which involve slamming your car into a direct frontal crash."},{"time":468000,"text":"But when you look at other types of crashes, like rear-impact crashes,"},{"time":470000,"text":"indeed, the car seats don't perform as well."},{"time":473000,"text":"And I think that's because they've been optimized to pass,"},{"time":475000,"text":"as we always expect people to do,"},{"time":477000,"text":"to optimize relative to bright-line rules"},{"time":479000,"text":"about how affected the car will be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":483000,"text":"And the other thing you might argue is,"},{"time":484000,"text":"\"Well, car seats have got a lot better over time."},{"time":486000,"text":"And so if we look at recent crashes --"},{"time":489000,"text":"the whole data set is almost 30 years' worth of data --"},{"time":491000,"text":"you won't see it in the recent crashes. The new car seats are far, far better.\""},{"time":493000,"text":"But indeed, in recent crashes the lap-and-shoulder seatbelts,"},{"time":497000,"text":"actually, are doing even better than the car seats."},{"time":500000,"text":"They say, \"Well, that's impossible, that can't be.\""},{"time":503000,"text":"And the line of argument, if you ask parents, is,"},{"time":505000,"text":"\"But car seats are so expensive and complicated,"},{"time":508000,"text":"and they have this big tangle of latches,"},{"time":511000,"text":"how could they possibly not work better than seatbelts"},{"time":514000,"text":"because they are so expensive and complicated?\""},{"time":516000,"text":"It's kind of an interesting logic,"},{"time":519000,"text":"I think, that people use. And the other logic, they say,"},{"time":522000,"text":"\"Well, the government wouldn't have told us [to] use them"},{"time":524000,"text":"if they weren't much better.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":526000,"text":"But what's interesting is the government telling us to use them"},{"time":528000,"text":"is not actually based on very much."},{"time":530000,"text":"It really is based on some impassioned pleas of parents"},{"time":533000,"text":"whose children died after they turned two,"},{"time":536000,"text":"which has led to the passage of all these laws -- not very much on data."},{"time":540000,"text":"So you can only get so far, I think, in telling your story"},{"time":544000,"text":"by using these abstract statistics."},{"time":546000,"text":"And so I had some friends over to dinner, and I was asking --"},{"time":551000,"text":"we had a cookout -- I was asking them what advice they might have for me"},{"time":554000,"text":"about proving my point. They said, \"Why don't you run some crash tests?\""},{"time":558000,"text":"And I said, \"That's a great idea.\""},{"time":560000,"text":"So we actually tried to commission some crash tests."},{"time":562000,"text":"And it turns out that as we called around to the independent"},{"time":567000,"text":"crash test companies around the country,"},{"time":570000,"text":"none of them wanted to do our crash test"},{"time":572000,"text":"because they said, some explicitly, some not so explicitly,"},{"time":576000,"text":"\"All of our business comes from car seat manufacturers."},{"time":578000,"text":"We can't risk alienating them by testing seatbelts relative to car seats.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":582000,"text":"Now, eventually, one did. Under the conditions of anonymity,"},{"time":586000,"text":"they said they would be happy to do this test for us --"},{"time":589000,"text":"so anonymity, and 1,500 dollars per seat that we crashed."},{"time":594000,"text":"And so, we went to Buffalo, New York,"},{"time":596000,"text":"and here is the precursor to it."},{"time":598000,"text":"These are the crash test dummies,"},{"time":600000,"text":"waiting for their chance to take the center stage."},{"time":603000,"text":"And then, here's how the crash test works."},{"time":605000,"text":"Here, they don't actually crash the entire car, you know --"},{"time":608000,"text":"it's not worth ruining a whole car to do it."},{"time":611000,"text":"So they just have these bench seats,"},{"time":612000,"text":"and they strap the car seat and the seatbelt onto it."},{"time":614000,"text":"So I just wanted you to look at this."},{"time":616000,"text":"And I think this gives you a good idea of why parents think"},{"time":618000,"text":"car seats are so great. Look at the kid in the car seat."},{"time":620000,"text":"Does he not look content, ready to go,"},{"time":623000,"text":"like he could survive anything? And then, if you look at the kid in back,"},{"time":625000,"text":"it looks like he's already choking before the crash even happens."},{"time":628000,"text":"It's hard to believe, when you look at this, that"},{"time":631000,"text":"that kid in back is going to do very well when you get in a crash."},{"time":633000,"text":"So this is going to be a crash"},{"time":635000,"text":"where they're going to slam this thing forward into a wall"},{"time":638000,"text":"at 30 miles an hour, and see what happens. OK?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":641000,"text":"So, let me show you what happens."},{"time":643000,"text":"These are three-year-old dummies, by the way."},{"time":646000,"text":"So here -- this is the car seat. Now watch two things:"},{"time":648000,"text":"watch how the head goes forward,"},{"time":650000,"text":"and basically hits the knees -- and this is in the car seat --"},{"time":652000,"text":"and watch how the car seat flies around, in the rebound, up in the air."},{"time":657000,"text":"The car seat's moving all over the place."},{"time":659000,"text":"Bear in mind there are two things about this."},{"time":661000,"text":"This is a car seat that was installed by someone"},{"time":664000,"text":"who has installed 1,000 car seats, who knew exactly how to do it."},{"time":667000,"text":"And also it turned out these bench seats"},{"time":668000,"text":"are the very best way to install car seats."},{"time":671000,"text":"Having a flat back makes it much easier to install them."},{"time":674000,"text":"And so this is a test that's very much rigged in favor of the car seat,"},{"time":677000,"text":"OK? So, that kid in this crash fared very well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":680000,"text":"The federal standards are"},{"time":682000,"text":"that you have to score below a 1,000"},{"time":684000,"text":"to be an approved car seat on this crash,"},{"time":686000,"text":"in some metric of units which are not important."},{"time":690000,"text":"And this crash would have been about a 450."},{"time":693000,"text":"So this car seat was actually an above-average car seat"},{"time":695000,"text":"from Consumer Reports, and did quite well."},{"time":697000,"text":"So the next one. Now, this is the kid, same crash,"},{"time":700000,"text":"who is in the seatbelt. He hardly moves at all, actually,"},{"time":705000,"text":"relative to the other child. The funny thing is,"},{"time":708000,"text":"the cam work is terrible because they've only set it up"},{"time":711000,"text":"to do the car seats, and so, they actually don't even have a way"},{"time":713000,"text":"to move the camera so you can see the kid that's on the rebound."},{"time":715000,"text":"Anyway, it turns out that those two crashes, that actually"},{"time":719000,"text":"the three-year-old did slightly worse. So, he gets about a 500"},{"time":723000,"text":"out of -- you know, on this range -- relative to a 400 and something."},{"time":727000,"text":"But still, if you just took that data from that crash"},{"time":730000,"text":"to the federal government, and said, \"I have invented a new car seat."},{"time":733000,"text":"I would like you to approve it for selling,\""},{"time":736000,"text":"then they would say, \"This is a fantastic new car seat, it works great."},{"time":739000,"text":"It only got a 500, it could have gotten as high up as a 1,000.\""},{"time":741000,"text":"And this seatbelt would have passed with flying colors"},{"time":744000,"text":"into being approved as a car seat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":746000,"text":"So, in some sense, what this is suggesting"},{"time":748000,"text":"is that it's not just that people are setting up their car seats wrong,"},{"time":751000,"text":"which is putting children at risk. It's just that, fundamentally,"},{"time":753000,"text":"the car seats aren't doing much."},{"time":755000,"text":"So here's the crash. So these are timed at the same time,"},{"time":757000,"text":"so you can see that it takes much longer with the car seat --"},{"time":759000,"text":"at rebound, it takes a lot longer --"},{"time":761000,"text":"but there's just a lot less movement for child who's in the seatbelt."},{"time":765000,"text":"So, I'll show you the six-year-old crashes as well."},{"time":767000,"text":"The six-year-old is in a car seat, and it turns out"},{"time":772000,"text":"that looks terrible, but that's great. That's like a 400, OK?"},{"time":777000,"text":"So that kid would do fine in the crash."},{"time":778000,"text":"Nothing about that would have been problematic to the child at all."},{"time":782000,"text":"And then here's the six-year-old in the seatbelt,"},{"time":785000,"text":"and in fact, they get exactly within, you know,"},{"time":787000,"text":"within one or two points of the same. So really, for the six-year-old,"},{"time":791000,"text":"the car seat did absolutely nothing whatsoever."}]},{"cues":[{"time":795000,"text":"That's some more evidence, so in some sense --"},{"time":798000,"text":"I was criticized by a scientist, who said, \"You could never publish"},{"time":802000,"text":"a study with an n of 4,\" meaning those four crashes."},{"time":804000,"text":"So I wrote him back and I said, \"What about an n of 45,004?\""},{"time":808000,"text":"Because I had the other 45,000 other real-world crashes."},{"time":810000,"text":"And I just think that it's interesting that the idea"},{"time":814000,"text":"of using real-world crashes, which is very much something"},{"time":816000,"text":"that economists think would be the right thing to do,"},{"time":818000,"text":"is something that scientists don't actually, usually think --"},{"time":820000,"text":"they would rather use a laboratory,"},{"time":823000,"text":"a very imperfect science of looking at the dummies,"},{"time":825000,"text":"than actually 30 years of data of what we've seen"},{"time":829000,"text":"with children and with car seats."}]},{"cues":[{"time":832000,"text":"And so I think the answer to this puzzle"},{"time":836000,"text":"is that there's a much better solution out there,"},{"time":839000,"text":"that's gotten nobody excited because everyone"},{"time":842000,"text":"is so delighted with the way car seats are presumably working."},{"time":846000,"text":"And if you think from a design perspective,"},{"time":849000,"text":"about going back to square one, and say,"},{"time":851000,"text":"\"I just want to protect kids in the back seat.\""},{"time":853000,"text":"I don't there's anyone in this room who'd say,"},{"time":855000,"text":"\"Well, the right way to start would be,"},{"time":856000,"text":"let's make a great seat belt for adults."},{"time":859000,"text":"And then, let's make this really big contraption"},{"time":861000,"text":"that you have to rig up to it in this daisy chain.\""},{"time":864000,"text":"I mean, why not start -- who's sitting in the back seat anyway except for kids?"},{"time":867000,"text":"But essentially, do something like this,"},{"time":870000,"text":"which I don't know exactly how much it would cost to do,"},{"time":872000,"text":"but there's no reason I could see"},{"time":873000,"text":"why this should be much more expensive than a regular car seat."},{"time":875000,"text":"It's just actually -- you see, this is folding up -- it's behind the seat."},{"time":879000,"text":"You've got a regular seat for adults, and then you fold it down,"},{"time":881000,"text":"and the kid sits on top, and it's integrated."},{"time":883000,"text":"It seems to me that this can't be a very expensive solution,"},{"time":887000,"text":"and it's got to work better than what we already have."}]},{"cues":[{"time":890000,"text":"So the question is, is there any hope for adoption of something like this,"},{"time":895000,"text":"which would presumably save a lot of lives?"},{"time":897000,"text":"And I think the answer, perhaps, lies in a story."},{"time":901000,"text":"The answer both to why has a car seat been so successful,"},{"time":905000,"text":"and why this may someday be adopted or not,"},{"time":908000,"text":"lies in a story that my dad told me, relating to when he was a doctor"},{"time":912000,"text":"in the U.S. Air Force in England. And this is a long time ago:"},{"time":915000,"text":"you were allowed to do things then you can't do today."},{"time":917000,"text":"So, my father would have patients come in"},{"time":921000,"text":"who he thought were not really sick."},{"time":924000,"text":"And he had a big jar full of placebo pills that he would give them,"},{"time":928000,"text":"and he'd say, \"Come back in a week, if you still feel lousy.\""},{"time":931000,"text":"OK, and most of them would not come back,"},{"time":932000,"text":"but some of them would come back."},{"time":934000,"text":"And when they came back, he, still convinced they were not sick,"},{"time":938000,"text":"had another jar of pills. In this jar were huge horse pills."},{"time":943000,"text":"They were almost impossible to swallow."},{"time":945000,"text":"And these, to me, are the analogy for the car seats."},{"time":949000,"text":"People would look at these and say, \"Man, this thing is so big"},{"time":953000,"text":"and so hard to swallow. If this doesn't make me feel better,"},{"time":955000,"text":"you know, what possibly could?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":958000,"text":"And it turned out that most people wouldn't come back,"},{"time":960000,"text":"because it worked. But every once in a while,"},{"time":963000,"text":"there was still a patient convinced that he was sick,"},{"time":968000,"text":"and he'd come back. And my dad had a third jar of pills."},{"time":971000,"text":"And the jar of pills he had, he said,"},{"time":973000,"text":"were the tiniest little pills he could find,"},{"time":976000,"text":"so small you could barely see them."},{"time":978000,"text":"And he would say, listen, I know I gave you that huge pill,"},{"time":980000,"text":"that complicated, hard-to-swallow pill before,"},{"time":984000,"text":"but now I've got one that's so potent,"},{"time":986000,"text":"that is really tiny and small and almost invisible."},{"time":988000,"text":"It's almost like this thing here, which you can't even see.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":991000,"text":"And it turned out that never,"},{"time":993000,"text":"in all the times my dad gave out this pill, the really tiny pill,"},{"time":996000,"text":"did anyone ever come back still complaining of sickness."},{"time":999000,"text":"So, my dad always took that as evidence"},{"time":1002000,"text":"that this little, teeny, powerful pill"},{"time":1006000,"text":"had the ultimate placebo effect. And in some sense, if that's the right story,"},{"time":1010000,"text":"I think integrated car seats you will see, very quickly,"},{"time":1012000,"text":"becoming something that everyone has. The other possible conclusion"},{"time":1016000,"text":"is, well, maybe after coming to my father three times,"},{"time":1019000,"text":"getting sent home with placebos, he still felt sick,"},{"time":1021000,"text":"he went and found another doctor."},{"time":1023000,"text":"And that's completely possible. And if that's the case,"},{"time":1025000,"text":"then I think we're stuck with conventional car seats for a long time to come."},{"time":1028000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1029000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1033000,"text":"(Audience: I just wanted to ask you, when we wear seatbelts"},{"time":1035000,"text":"we don't necessarily wear them just to prevent loss of life,"},{"time":1038000,"text":"it's also to prevent lots of serious injury."},{"time":1040000,"text":"Your data looks at fatalities. It doesn't look at serious injury."},{"time":1044000,"text":"Is there any data to show that child seats"},{"time":1046000,"text":"are actually less effective, or just as effective as seatbelts"},{"time":1049000,"text":"for serious injury? Because that would prove your case.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1051000,"text":"Steven Levitt: Yeah, that's a great question. In my data, and in another data set"},{"time":1054000,"text":"I've looked at for New Jersey crashes,"},{"time":1057000,"text":"I find very small differences in injury."},{"time":1061000,"text":"So in this data, it's statistically insignificant differences"},{"time":1063000,"text":"in injury between car seats and lap-and-shoulder belts."},{"time":1067000,"text":"In the New Jersey data, which is different,"},{"time":1068000,"text":"because it's not just fatal crashes,"},{"time":1071000,"text":"but all crashes in New Jersey that are reported,"},{"time":1073000,"text":"it turns out that there is a 10 percent difference in injuries,"},{"time":1076000,"text":"but generally they're the minor injuries."},{"time":1078000,"text":"Now, what's interesting, I should say this as a disclaimer,"},{"time":1080000,"text":"there is medical literature that is very difficult to resolve with this other data,"},{"time":1085000,"text":"which suggests that car seats are dramatically better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1089000,"text":"And they use a completely different methodology that involves --"},{"time":1091000,"text":"after the crash occurs, they get from the insurance companies"},{"time":1094000,"text":"the names of the people who were in the crash,"},{"time":1096000,"text":"and they call them on the phone,"},{"time":1097000,"text":"and they asked them what happened."},{"time":1098000,"text":"And I really can't resolve, yet,"},{"time":1101000,"text":"and I'd like to work with these medical researchers"},{"time":1103000,"text":"to try to understand how there can be these differences,"},{"time":1106000,"text":"which are completely at odds with one another."},{"time":1109000,"text":"But it's obviously a critical question."},{"time":1112000,"text":"The question is even if -- are there enough serious injuries"},{"time":1115000,"text":"to make these cost-effective? It's kind of tricky."},{"time":1118000,"text":"Even if they're right, it's not so clear"},{"time":1120000,"text":"that they're so cost-effective."}]}]}